'''旋角牛'''（[[學名|學名]]：{{lang|la|''Pseudonovibos spiralis''}}）是[[柬埔寨|柬埔寨]]及[[越南|越南]]的一種[[牛科|牛科]]动物，也是'''旋角牛属'''的唯一已知物种，由於實証不足，其真實性至今存疑。

==特徵==
旋角牛最初被認為是像[[牛|牛]]的[[動物|動物]]，有著一對長約45厘米及扭曲的角，身上有斑點。

==名稱==
旋角牛的[[柬埔寨|柬埔寨]]名字“kting voar”最初被西方譯為「叢林綿羊」，故被誤會是一種與[[羊|羊]]有關的[[動物|動物]]。這個柬埔寨名字事實上是「角像籐一般的野牛」。由於混淆，[[越南|越南]]曾有报告稱牠們在当地的為名字“[[羚羊|羚羊]]”，但其實那是當地人對[[鬣羚|鬣羚]]的稱呼。

旋角牛的[[學名|學名]]“''Pseudonovibos spiralis''”並不有效，因為其[[完模標本|完模標本]]其實是一隻[[家牛|家牛]]，而此學名的字面意思正好是「有旋角的偽家牛」。

==爭議==
最初支持旋角牛存在的證據是[[沃爾夫岡·皮特|沃爾夫岡·皮特]]（Wolfgang Peter）在[[胡志明市|胡志明市]]市場購來的一些角。<ref name=PeterFeiler1994a>{{Cite journal|author=Peter, W.P., Feiler, A.|year=1994a|title=Horns of an unknown bovid species from Vietnam (Mammalia: Ruminantia)|journal=Faun. Abh. Mus. Tierkd. Dresden|volume=19|pages=247–53}}</ref> 皮特認為這些角屬於一個新的[[物種|物種]]。<ref name=PeterFeiler1994b>{{Cite journal|author=Peter, W.P., Feiler, A.|year=1994b|title=A new bovid species from Vietnam and Cambodia (Mammalia: Ruminantia)|journal=Zool. Abh. Mus. Tierkd. Dresden|volume=48|pages=169–76}}</ref>

由於沒有解剖資料，旋角牛的[[種系發生學|種系發生學]]地位不明。皮特等人建議將旋角牛分類到[[羚羊族|羚羊族]]中<ref name=PeterFeiler1994a/>，但從形態分析卻指牠們應屬於[[牛族|牛族]]<ref name=Dioli1995>{{Cite journal|author=Dioli M.|year=1995|title=A clarification about the morphology of the horns of the female kouprey: a new unknown bovid species from Cambodia|journal=Mammalia|volume=59|pages=663–7}}</ref><ref name=Dioli1997>{{Cite journal|author=Dioli, M.|year=1997|title=Notes on the morphology of the horns of a new artiodactyl mammal from Cambodia: ''Pseudonovibos spiralis''|journal=J. Zool. (Lond.)|volume=241|pages=527–31}}</ref><ref name=TimmBrandt2001>{{Cite journal|author=Timm, R.M. & Brandt, J.H.|year=2001|title=''Pseudonovibos spiralis'' (Artiodactyla: Bovidae): new information on this enigmatic South-east Asian ox|journal=J. Zool., Lond.|volume=253|pages=157–66}}</ref>，更有學者認為是[[羊族|羊族]]。<ref name=Nadler1997>{{Cite journal|author=Nadler, T.|year=1997|title=Was ist ''Pseudonovibos spiralis''?|journal=Zool. Garten N.F.|volume=67|pages=290–2}}</ref>[[遺傳學|遺傳學]]分析卻造成了更混淆的結果。<ref name=Hammer1999>{{Cite journal|author=Hammer, S.E., Suchentrunk, F., Tiedemann, R., Hartl, G.B., Feiler, A.|year=1999|title=Mitochondrial DNA sequence relationships of the newly described enigmatic Vietnamese bovid, ''Pseudonovibos spiralis''|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_naturwissenschaften_1999-06_86_6/page/279|journal=Naturwissenschaften|volume=86|pages=279–80}}</ref><ref name=Kuznetsov2001a>{{Cite journal|author=Kuznetsov, G.V., Kulikov, E.E., Petrov, N.B., Ivanova, N.V., Lomov, A.A., Kholodova, M.V., Poltaraus, A.B.|year=2001a|title=The "linh duong" ''Pseudonovibos spiralis'' (Mammalia, Artiodactyla) is a new buffalo|journal=Naturwissenschaften|volume=88|pages=123–5}}</ref><ref name=Kuznetsov2001b>{{Cite journal|author=Kuznetsov, G.V., Kulikov, E.E., Petrov, N.B., Ivanova, N.V., Lomov, A.A., Kholodova, M.V., Poltaraus, A.B.|year=2001b|title=Taxonomic status and phylogenetic relations of the new genus and species ''Pseudonovibos spiralis'' W.P. Peter, A. Feiler, 1994 (Artiodactyla, Bovidae)|journal=Zoologičeskij Žurnal|volume=80|issue=11|pages=1395–403}}</ref><ref name=Kuznetsov2002>{{Cite journal|author=Kuznetsov, G.V., Kulikov, E.E., Petrov, N.B., Ivanova, N.V., Lomov, A.A., Kholodova, M.V., Poltaraus, A.B.|year=2002|title=Mitochondrial 12S rDNA sequence relationships suggest that the enigmatic bovid "linh duong" ''Pseudonovibos spiralis'' is closely related to buffalo|journal=Mol. Phylogenet. Evol.|volume=23|issue=1|pages=91–4}}</ref> 不過這些[[DNA|DNA]]明顯是受到了污染。<ref name=HassaninDouzery2000>{{Cite journal|author=Hassanin, A., Douzery, E.|year=2000|title=Is the newly described bovid, ''Pseudonovibos spiralis'', a chamois (genus ''Rupicapra'')?|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_naturwissenschaften_2000-03_87_3/page/122|journal=Naturwissenschaften|volume=87|pages=122–4}}</ref><ref name=Hassanin2002>{{Cite journal|author=Hassanin, A.|year=2002|title=Ancient specimens and DNA contamination: a case study from the 12S rRNA gene sequence of the "linh duong" bovid (''Pseudonovibos spiralis'')|journal=Naturwissenschaften|volume=89|pages=107–10}}</ref><ref name=OlsonHassanin2003>{{Cite journal|author=Olson, L. E. and Hassanin A.|year=2003|title=Contamination and chimerism are perpetuating the legend of the snake-eating cow with twisted horns (''Pseudonovibos spiralis''): A case study of the pitfalls of ancient DNA|journal=Mol. Phylogenetics. Evol.|volume=27|issue=2|pages=545–8}}</ref> 所有相信是屬於旋角牛及用來進行DNA測試的標本，其實都是人工製成的[[家牛|家牛]]牛角。<ref name=Hassanin2002/><ref name=Hassanin2001>{{Cite journal|author=Hassanin, A., Seveau, A., Thomas, H., Bocherens, H., Billiou, D. and Nguyen, B.X.|year=2001|title=Evidence from DNA that the mysterious 'linh duong' (''Pseudonovibos spiralis'') is not a new bovid|journal=Comptes Rendus de l'Académie des Sciences Série III Sciences de la Vie|volume=324|pages=71–80}}</ref>

懷疑者都認為旋角牛只是傳說的動物，但也有學者認為傳說的本身可能代表著一種野生[[牛族|牛族]]的存在。<ref name=TimmBrandt2001/><ref name=Brandt2001>{{Cite journal|author=Brandt, J. H., Dioli, M., Hassanin, A., Melville, R. A., Olson, L. E., Seveau, A., and Timm, R. M.|year=2001|title=Debate on the authenticity of ''Pseudonovibos spiralis'' as a new species of wild bovid from Vietnam and Cambodia|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-zoology_2001-12_255/page/437|journal=Journal of Zoology|volume=255|pages=437–44}}</ref> 若後者是真的，旋角牛應是十分[[瀕危|瀕危]]或甚至已經[[滅絕|滅絕]]。

